data.description: Elegance defined! This stunning, single-level home sits on a corner lot in an ideal location just minutes from the lake & beaches, and offers comfort & sophistication with beautiful indoor and outdoor living spaces, plus features OWNED solar, a full house Generac generator in case of PSPS, an oversized 3 car garage plus multiple driveway parking spaces, and lush landscaping. Enter to find gorgeous hard wood flooring, soaring ceilings & a grand and open great room. The spacious living room enjoys plush carpeting, a free-standing gas fireplace for both warmth & ambiance, and large picture windows. Host dinner parties from the comfort of the upgraded kitchen with its stainless steel appliances including a five burner propane cooktop, beautiful cabinetry, large pantry, and a breakfast bar with a convenient salad sink. All three bedrooms are oversized with high ceilings plus an extra wide hallway. The bathrooms feature lovely custom tile work and vanities, with dual sinks, a soaking tub and stall shower in the primary suite and an oversized tub/shower in the hall bath. 3+ car garage with extra deep bays plus a large pull through driveway for plenty of parking. Gorgeous landscaped yard & covered patio areas. Lifetime roof, surround sound & more! Buyer incentives available!
